physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Physical examination revealed diminished strength in lower limbs: 2/5 in the right pelvic limb and 3/5 proximal and 2/5 distal in the left pelvic limb. Sensitive affection with hypoesthesia located in the T6 dermatome. Patellar and Achilles stretch reflexes were poorly evoked. The rest of the examination was normal.
